Barclays CEO Diamond in Talks to Buy Spanish Bank, Times Says

-- B y   G a v i n   F i n c h
-- 
2011-05-29T13:38:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/barclays-ceo-in-talks-to-buy-spanish-regional-bank-times-says.html
Barclays Plc (BARC) ’s Chief Executive
Officer  Robert Diamond  is in talks to buy one of  Spain ’s
regional banks, the  Sunday Times  reported, without saying where
it got the information.  Diamond met with Spanish Prime Minister Jose Luis Rodriguez Zapatero in  Madrid  last week to discuss the plan to buy the
unidentified bank, the newspaper reported.  Giles Croot, a spokesman for Barclays, declined to comment
when contacted by Bloomberg News.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gavin Finch in London at 
